data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This spacious and modern 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom house boasts over 2600+ square feet of luxurious living space. Step inside and be greeted by beautiful modern updates throughout the home, including a bright stunning kitchen, stylish light fixtures, and sleek bathrooms. This home offers ample space for the entire family, with four generously sized bathrooms which provide comfort and privacy. Additionally, an extra loft area awaits, perfect for transforming into a game room for the kids or a cozy entertainment space. Solar system in place to help save with the electricity bill. Step outside and discover a huge backyard that has been meticulously landscaped, which offers a serene oasis for relaxation and entertainment. The covered patio provides an ideal spot for outdoor gatherings and enjoying the fresh air. Living in this community means enjoying an abundance of amenities. Take advantage of the tennis courts for some friendly competition, cool off in the pool on hot summer days, unwind in the spa and host memorable bbq parties in the designated areas. Additionally, nearby parks offer opportunities for outdoor activities or strolls around the lake. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a beautifully updated home!
